org.bonitasoft.engine.bpm.process

Interface Problem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable

    public interface Problem
extends Serializable
    A Problem explains the issue in the DesignProcessDefinition when it is not well designed. It relates to :
    • structural problems such as a BoundaryEventDefinition without an exception flow,
    • naming problems such as two FlowNodeDefinitions with the same name,
    • type problems such as an Expression which has not the right type,
    • ...
    Since:
    6.0.0
    Version:
    6.3.5
    Author:
    Matthieu Chaffotte, Celine Souchet
